---
/* C_main — GEO 方法论区（Analyze → Execute → Feedback） */
---

<section id="methodology" class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24 mx-auto">
  <!-- Grid -->
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
    
    <!-- 左列：方法论说明 + 案例语句 -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-1">
      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold lg:text-4xl dark:text-gray-200">
          GEO 方法论：从分析到放大
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          奇点GEO 的核心逻辑由 <strong>语义诊断 → 内容重构 → 反馈追踪</strong> 三步构成。
          每一步都围绕「AI 可见度」这一目标持续优化，让品牌内容被更多AI搜索准确识别与推荐。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 三步逻辑流程 -->
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex gap-x-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 id="analyze" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">语义诊断（Analyze）</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
              对目标关键词、语义簇和平台信源进行多模型分析，识别内容缺口与潜在引用机会。
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-x-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 id="execute" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">内容重构（Execute）</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
              基于 GEO-Score 与品牌专属逻辑链，对内容进行重写与结构强化，提升 AI 兼容度。
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-x-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 id="feedback" class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">反馈追踪（Feedback）</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
              及时监测模型端引用数据与关键词触达表现，动态调整策略以提升排名与信任度。
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Testimonial -->
      <blockquote class="relative mt-10">
        <svg class="absolute top-0 left-0 transform -translate-x-6 -translate-y-8 h-16 w-16 text-gray-200 dark:text-gray-800"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path
            d="M7.39762 10.3C7.39762 11.0733 7.14888 11.7 6.6514 12.18C6.15392 12.6333 5.52552 12.86 4.76621 12.86C3.84979 12.86 3.09047 12.5533 2.48825 11.94C1.91222 11.3266 1.62421 10.4467 1.62421 9.29999C1.62421 8.07332 1.96459 6.87332 2.64535 5.69999C3.35231 4.49999 4.33418 3.55332 5.59098 2.85999L6.4943 4.25999C5.81354 4.73999 5.26369 5.27332 4.84476 5.85999C4.45201 6.44666 4.19017 7.12666 4.05926 7.89999C4.29491 7.79332 4.56983 7.73999 4.88403 7.73999C5.61716 7.73999 6.21938 7.97999 6.69067 8.45999C7.16197 8.93999 7.39762 9.55333 7.39762 10.3Z"
            fill="currentColor" />
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-xl italic text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
            “在接入 奇点GEO 后，我们的品牌内容首次出现在通义与百度 AI 搜索推荐中。”
          </p>
        </div>
        <footer class="mt-6">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <img class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full"
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502685104226-ee32379fefbe?auto=format&fit=facearea&w=320&h=320&q=80"
              alt="User avatar" />
            <div class="ml-3">
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">陈璟 | 品牌总监</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Fengheju Traditional Apparel</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- 右列：指标数据 -->
    <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-end-13">
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 divide-y divide-y-2 divide-x divide-x-2 divide-gray-200 overflow-hidden dark:divide-gray-700 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
        <li class="flex flex-col -m-0.5 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">+68%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">平均 AI 呈现率提升</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex flex-col -m-0.5 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">+41%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">引用/推荐次数增长</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex flex-col -m-0.5 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">3x</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">AI 搜索曝光效率</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex flex-col -m-0.5 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-gray-200">92%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">内容 GEO 评分提升</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ✅ Schema for GEO Methodology -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HowTo",
    "name": "奇点GEO 方法论：三步提升品牌 AI 可见度",
    "description": "通过语义诊断（Analyze）、内容重构（Execute）与反馈追踪（Feedback）三步，系统性优化品牌在生成式搜索与多模型生态中的可见度。",
    "url": "https://oldriver.work/#method",
    "mainEntityOfPage": "https://oldriver.work",
    "image": "https://oldriver.work/geo-method-cover.png",
    "step": [
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "name": "语义诊断（Analyze）",
        "url": "https://oldriver.work/#analyze",
        "text": "识别品牌相关的关键词语义簇、场景问题与引用机会，分析各主流 AI 模型中的内容呈现情况，找出语义缺口和信源弱点。"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "name": "内容重构（Execute）",
        "url": "https://oldriver.work/#execute",
        "text": "基于诊断结果，重写与重构核心内容，统一结构化表达、引用证明与 Schema 标注，使内容更易被模型索引、理解与引用。"
      },
      {
        "@type": "HowToStep",
        "name": "反馈追踪（Feedback）",
        "url": "https://oldriver.work/#feedback",
        "text": "通过监测搜索结果、AI 回复样本与引用频次，持续评估 GEO 效果，并按周期调整内容与信源布局，形成闭环优化。"
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

</section>
